snippet.title: Skellboy: Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Fabraz is proud to publish Skellboy, by Umaiki Games, to the Nintendo Switch in 2019! 

http://fabraz.com/p_skellboy.html

This is early alpha footage and everything's subject to change.
